DISMANTLE

Usage:  dismantle
Speed boosts:  Faster Chores bonus, haste

This command allows you to tear down a building when you're done with it. You
get back approximately half of the resources you spent to build it, although
dismantle can only refund items that were used -- it can't refund any coins,
mana, or liquids that were spent.

You can use "nodismantle" to keep yourself from accidentally dismantling a
building.

See also: BUILD, NODISMANTLE
