GATHER

Gather (Scavenging ability)

Usage:  gather
Speed boosts:  Faster Chores bonus, Finder ability, Haste

Allows you to gather sticks from the ground. Your skill in this determines
how many different sticks you can use and thus how quickly you gather enough.

You can also gather apples in an orchard.

See also: DEPLETION, STICKS, APPLES, ORCHARD, SCAVENGING
